<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Désinscription newsletter</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #353535;
        background-color: rgba(53, 53, 53, 0.1);
    }
    .container{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;   
    }
    h1{
        background-color: #353535;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-top: 0;
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    h1, h2 {
        text-align: center;
    }



</style>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bonjour Christiane !</h1>
        <p>Vous avez un nouveau message de {{ message.name }}-{{ message.surname }} en date du {{ message.createdAt|date("d/m/Y H:m:s") }}</p>
        <h3>Sujet : </h3><p>{{ message.subject}}</p>
        <h3>Message : </h3><p>{{ message.content }}</p>
        <section>
        <p>Pour répondre à ce message, merci de cliquer sur le lien suivant :<a href="{{ message.email }}">{{ message.email }}</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>